      <description>Nothing is more fashionable and feminine than this Acer Aspire Notebook Case in Pink Faux Alligator Skin.  This is the perfect pink laptop carrying case for a girl who wants to look good and feel comfortable while carrying around a laptop.  The pink faux alligator skin makes this case look trendy to go along with [...]&lt;p&gt;Post from: &lt;a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com"&gt;Pink Laptop Diva&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/pink-laptop-diva/Pink_Laptop_Diva-Acer_Aspire_One_Foam_Pink_Netbook_Case_Review.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignleft size-full wp-image-222" title="pink laptop foam case" src="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/aspire_one_pink_netbook_foam_case.jpg" alt="pink laptop foam case" width="280" height="280" />Nothing is more fashionable and feminine than this <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/03/acer-aspire-one-pink-netbook-review/" >Acer Aspire</a> Notebook Case in Pink Faux Alligator Skin.  This is the perfect <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/06/pink-laptop/" >pink laptop</a> carrying case for a girl who wants to look good and feel comfortable while carrying around a laptop.  The pink faux alligator skin makes this case look trendy to go along with all your other stylish accessories and outfit.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/03/acer-aspire-one-pink-netbook-review/" >Acer Aspire</a> laptop case can hold laptops up to 8.9 inches while providing safety and security.  It features a premium quality shock absorbing double memory foam pouch to keep your notebook protected in all conditions.  To add in more stability, there are internal supporting bands to keep your laptop in its place while you are moving around. It is also water resistant in case you are stuck in the rain and has a zipper scratch-free exterior.<span id="more-220"></span></p>
<p>With the ultra light and very thin design of this laptop case, you can carry your laptop around with comfort and ease.  The padded shoulder strap is comfy and also detachable if you want to use it like a briefcase.  You can even match it to any of the <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/06/pink-laptop/" >pink laptops</a> that are very popular these days. This <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/06/pink-laptop/" >pink laptop</a> case in pink is the perfect companion for a girl who is constantly on the go for school, travel and work.</p>
