      <description>The Sony VAIO Lifestyle pink laptop is the perfect-sized accessory to put in your trendy tote bag whether you are going to school or work.  Weighing only 1.4 pounds, the Sony VAIO Lifestyle comes in a flashy Garnet Red color for good looks. It features an 8 inch ultra-wide high resolution LED backlit screen that [...]&lt;p&gt;Post from: &lt;a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com"&gt;Pink Laptop Diva&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;a type="audio/mpeg" href="http://podcasts.odiogo.com/get_mp3.mp3?f=/pink-laptop-diva/Pink_Laptop_Diva-Sony_VAIO_Lifestyle_Pink_Laptop_Review.mp3"&gt;Click here to play&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br&gt;</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-181" title="Sony Lifestyle Pink Netbook" src="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/04/sony_lifestyle-300x210.jpg" alt="Sony Lifestyle Pink Netbook" width="300" height="210" />The <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/04/sony-vaio-lifestyle-pink-laptop-review/" >Sony VAIO</a> Lifestyle <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/06/pink-laptop/" >pink laptop</a> is the perfect-sized accessory to put in your trendy tote bag whether you are going to school or work.  Weighing only 1.4 pounds, the <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/04/sony-vaio-lifestyle-pink-laptop-review/" >Sony VAIO</a> Lifestyle comes in a flashy Garnet Red color for good looks. It features an 8 inch ultra-wide high resolution LED backlit screen that displays crisp and clear graphics and is wide enough so you don’t have to scroll side to side anymore.  It also has a built-in GPS navigation to find a happening restaurant or café to check out, and you don’t even need internet connection to access it.</p>
<p>This compact pink notebook is made for advanced computing and communicating for anyone who wants to travel with their computer. It features a built-in wireless WAN 3G Mobile Broadband access so that you can have internet on the go to chat with your friends, go shopping, download music and do research. It even has Wi-Fi and Bluetooth technology. <span id="more-179"></span>This P Series Lifestyle by Sony comes with Windows Vista with essential software programs already installed including Microsoft Office.  The power system has an Intel 1.33 GHz Processor with a 60 Gig hard drive and built in shock protection.  Other specifications include 2 GB RAM, memory stick slots, SD Card slots, and a built-in webcam and microphone.</p>
<p>The <a href="http://www.pinklaptopdiva.com/2009/04/sony-vaio-lifestyle-pink-laptop-review/" >Sony VAIO</a> P Series Lifestyle is as thin and compact as your cell phone and can last up to four hours on a battery.  It not only gives you everything a regular laptop provides, but it also helps you organize all your open windows and documents on a wide screen with just a press of a button. With this notebook, you have the lightest computer to do almost anything at any location.</p>
